Title: A Measurement of the Fluorescence Efficiency of Air  
Author: F.Kakimoto E.C.Loh M.Nagano H.Okuno M.Teshima and T.Ueno 
Address: Tokyo 152  Salt Lake City UT84112, USA  Tokyo, Tokyo 188  Tokyo, Tokyo 188  
